                                   rdfs:label "RobustMeanAbsoluteDeviation" ;
                                   <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The mean absolute deviation feature may be influenced by outliers. To increase robustness, the set of grey levels can be restricted to those which lie closer to the center of the distribution." .


