<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/CINW> rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                   rdfs:subClassOf :ImageFeatureSpace ;
                                   rdfs:label "Feature Parameter Space" ;
                                   <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The feature parameter space is defined as the space that includes all the possible radiomics computation methods that can be applied to certain radiomics features. Subclasses are: aggregation re-segmentation, interpolation, features specific parameters, discretization" .


###  http://www.radiomics.org/RO/CMWE
