                                   rdfs:label "GLDM_LowDependenceLowGreyLevelEmphasis" ;
                                   <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "This feature emphasises neighbouring grey level dependence counts in the upper left quad- rant of the NGLDM, where low dependence counts and low grey levels are located" .


