                                   rdfs:subClassOf <http://www.radiomics.org/RO/UHIW> ;
                                   rdfs:isDefinedBy "IBSI" ;
                                   rdfs:label "InterquartileRange" ;
                                   <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The interquartile range (IQR) is defined as P75 - P25, where P75 is the 75th percentile of the image matrix, and P25 is the 25th" .


###  http://www.radiomics.org/RO/SKGS
<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/SKGS> rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                   rdfs:subClassOf <http://www.radiomics.org/RO/HCUG> ;
                                   rdfs:isDefinedBy "IBSI" ;
                                   rdfs:label "Compactness1" ;
                                   <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The Compactness defines the deviation of the ROI volume from a perfect sphere. Compactness 1 is a measure of how compact, or sphere-like or sphere like the volume is" .


