###  http://www.radiomics.org/RO/Y1RO
<http://www.radiomics.org/RO/Y1RO> rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                   rdfs:subClassOf <http://www.radiomics.org/RO/9SAK> ;
                                   rdfs:isDefinedBy "IBSI" ;
                                   rdfs:label "GLSZM_GreyLevelNonUniformityNormalised" ;
